  "trivia_items": [
    "Garrett Graham's tattoo in the 2026 Off Campus series reads \"Nullum Gratuitum Prandium\" across his shoulder blades. This Latin phrase translates to \"there is no free lunch,\" signifying that everything in life has a cost and must be earned, reflecting his dedication to self-sufficiency and hard work",
    "Off Campus is renewed for a second season before the first season's release day.",
    "Season 1 of Off Campus focused primarily on The Deal, the first book in the series by Elle Kennedy. It also introduces a secondary storyline from The Score, book 3"
